# Coding standards

- Server Components default; `"use client"` only for state/effects/events
- `await params` / `await searchParams` (Promises in Next 16)
- `type` for props; strict TS; no `any`
- `<Link>` / `<Image>` — except LCP hero (`HeroSection` + `LcpImagePreload`)
- `pageMetadata()` for all `generateMetadata`; `[...slug]` → `join('/')`
- GROQ only in `sanity/lib/queries.ts` via `safeFetch` — see `04-sanity.mdc`
- No Sanity/nodemailer in client components
- Styling → `06-tailwind.mdc` · RTL copy → `03-rtl-urdu.mdc`
- Naming → `15-naming.mdc` · DRY → `16-dry.mdc` · Layout → `14-file-structure.mdc`
- API routes → `17-security.mdc` · Zod schemas in `lib/`
- Portable Text body → `components/content/RichTextBody.tsx` + `TW_RICH_TEXT_*`

Full naming tables: **`15-naming.mdc`**. Summary below for quick reference only.

## Quick naming (see 15 for authority)

- Components: `PascalCase.tsx`; lib/sanity: `camelCase.ts`
- Props: `type ComponentNameProps` · fetchers: `get*` · handlers: `handle*` (client only)
- GROQ exports: `camelCaseQuery` · fragments: `SCREAMING_SNAKE`
